item.title: Review of Sunset Bay Lakehouse Cabin 3 Bed 2 Bath – Amazing views! by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: This house never fails to be just perfect! It's very clean, the beds are comfy, the shower is great and its location can't be beat! The kitchen is also well-stocked with anything you'd need.
The floors are pretty creaky, but that is to be expected in an older house :)

item.title: Review of Luxury Cabin! 2Bed/3Bath – Gorgeous Views and Spacious Decks by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: This house has it all! Comfy beds, a perfect location and on those really hot, sticky days, it has enough air conditioning to cool off the upstairs, too :)
The floors are pretty creaky, but that is to be expected in an older house :)

item.title: Review of Gold Coast Wow Celebrity Themed Unit On Cedar! by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: This neighborhood is really cute and family friendly. There are little shops, coffee and restaurants within walking distance.
The drive to downtown is quite bad.

item.title: Review of Great Family Retreat in Lincoln Square *Free WiFi *Back Patio *Grill *Cable TV by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: The children played in the basement, we cooked and ate most meals in the cottage, and the upstairs bedrooms and bath are thoughtfully appointed with extra pillows, blankets, toilet paper, step stool, and laundry basket. The location is ideal for walking to multiple playgrounds and we loved the little lending libraries in front of various houses.
Suggest non-skid strips in the bathtub and more comfortable seating on the back porch - otherwise, it's a great place to stay

item.title: Review of Gorgeous Oceanfront Apt Steps From The Beach, Air Conditioned, Free Wi-Fi by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: The beds are comfortable, the kitchen is bright and functional. It was cozy, quiet and worked well for us.
Instructions for the dish washer would have been helpful.

item.title: Review of Rivers Peak Cabins – Private Romantic Cabin for (2) with great views by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: The house is very clean, well decorated, well equipped, very functional. The owners are very nice and helpful, they answered to all our questions.

item.title: Review of Luxury Lorelei 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Near Beach and El by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: It was clean, charming, and conveniently located. It was a short drive into the city but provided a quiet and comfortable place to sleep.
I only wish the place was just a tad larger so that we could accommodate a slightly larger group on our next trip.

item.title: Review of Family Vacation Rental with Suburban + great pool & short walk to the beach by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Location couldn't have been better. The beds were extremely comfortable and there was plenty of room to spread out. Loved that we had a garage to park in.
Can't say enough. Look forward to staying again.

item.title: Review of New Luxury Remodel, Ocean End, Right Over the Beach! by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Fabulous time spent at this beautiful home. Excellent accommodations, lovely pool and hot tub.
About a mile to the downtown area and a mile to the beach, which is a bit far.

item.title: Review of 2BR 2BA World Resort Condo, Newly Updated units! 3Blocks to Gate! by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: It's a wonderful, well-decorated home and property with responsive and accommodating hosts. Convenient/short drive to great restaurants and bars. Comfortable beds and well-appointed kitchen.
Unfortunately, poor weather did not allow us to experience the outdoor spaces.

item.title: Review of Luxury home with spectacular pool. Near wineries, walk to the village! by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: This house in the perfect location for a getaway. We had a great time and would love to visit in the summer.
Unfortunately, poor weather did not allow us to experience the outdoor spaces.

item.title: Review of Beautiful 3 bedrooms, 2 full Baths, spacious, elegant, spotless, next to pool by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Did I say clean,clean and double clean. Bedding is quality. This was nicer than any bed and breakfast I ever stayed in. They take care about delivering a quality product. No penny pinching! They go the extra mile to deliver class.

item.title: Review of Brand new Renovation in Historic District with 2 parking spots -walk everywhere by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: We had an amazing family vacation there. The owners were accommodating and delightful to work with. Close to town and located in a quiet neighborhood.
Overall, the house is OK, but not really worth the money.

item.title: Review of Brand new Renovation in Historic District with 2 parking spots -walk everywhere by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: We had an amazing family vacation there. The owners were accommodating and delightful to work with. Close to town and located in a quiet neighborhood.
Overall, the house is OK, but not really worth the money.

item.title: Review of Oak Park Cottage – Walk to Frank Lloyd Wright Home and Studio by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: What made it awesome was the lovely modern HOUSE and the lovely spacious yard. The kids had a blast running around in the yard - coming from the city where we have zero outdoor space - this is a BIG treat for us!
There was an ant problem at the time of our stay.

item.title: Review of Learn to take better travel photos by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: I was so at ease the entire time. He was so willing to listen to my ideas, had such an eye for unique shots, and was more than accommodating. If you're wanting high caliber photos for any purpose, this experience comes with high praise from me.

item.title: Review of Experience the night life with the locals by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Great pub crawl tour with about 15 people from all over the world, both tourists and locals. A perfect host, a very social and enthusiastic person, making sure everyone was integrated and enjoying themselves. The bars and the club were well selected and transitions between places was timed well. Would definitely recommend for people travelling alone and looking for a great night out, but also for couples or small group of friends wanting to socialize and meet new people.

item.title: Review of A historic tour around the Golden Gate bridge by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: There were great and engaging stories told by our very kind and friendly tour guide. It was very educational about history, but also the fun kind of history stories.
Our group lost energy by the end, especially when one of the bikes got a flat tire.

item.title: Review of Indulgent retro beach picnic in San Francisco by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: This experience is amazing!! Marine is a really nice person, the food is incredible. 100% I would recommend this experience and of course I would take it again.
Windy weather spoiled the fun a little.

item.title: Review of Vista Bay 3 Bedroom – Next To Intl Convention Center – Sunset by admin [1]
item.dc:creator: admin

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Right in the residential neighborhood. Close to Metro, and to supermarket.
Not close to restaurants and nightlife.
